          <li><font size="2" face="Arial">Click the check box of the respective
           Year/Semester in the select menu.</font></li>
          <li><font size="2" face="Arial">Edit the Year/Semester name in
          the text box and click button Modify to update the details.</font></li>
          <li><font size="2" face="Arial">Click button Delete to the delete
           the Year/Semester.</font></li>
